Module Management

13. Disable Problematic Modules
# Disable specific modules
php bin/magento module:disable Module_Name --force

# Disable all Amasty modules
php bin/magento module:disable Amasty_CheckoutStyleSwitcher Amasty_Checkout Amasty_CheckoutCore Amasty_CheckoutDeliveryDate Amasty_CheckoutProPackage Amasty_OneStepCheckoutProSubscriptionPackage --force

# Check module status
php bin/magento module:status

# Re-enable modules
php bin/magento module:enable Module_Name

# Disable all Amasty modules
php bin/magento module:disable Amasty_CheckoutStyleSwitcher Amasty_Checkout Amasty_CheckoutCore Amasty_CheckoutDeliveryDate Amasty_CheckoutProPackage Amasty_OneStepCheckoutProSubscriptionPackage --force

# Check module status
php bin/magento module:status

# Re-enable modules
php bin/magento module:enable Module_Name

14.  Fix Amasty Module Issues
# Remove problematic CSS
rm -rf app/code/Amasty/Base/view/frontend/web/css

# Or rename module temporarily
mv app/code/Amasty/CheckoutDeliveryDate app/code/Amasty_CheckoutDeliveryDate.disabled

Post-Upgrade Commands
15. Compile and Reindex

# Remove generated files
rm -rf generated/* var/di/* var/generation/*

# Compile
php -d memory_limit=8G bin/magento setup:di:compile

# Reindex all
php bin/magento indexer:reindex

# Reindex specific
php bin/magento indexer:reindex catalog_product_price catalog_product_category

16. Clear Cache
bash
php bin/magento cache:clean
php bin/magento cache:flush

17. Disable Maintenance Mode
bash
php bin/magento maintenance:disable

Verification Commands
